Class RDFPropertyPrototype

  • java.lang.Object
    • gate.gui.ontology.RDFPropertyPrototype
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OResource, RDFProperty

     class RDFPropertyPrototype
extends Object
implements RDFProperty
    An empty impl of RDFProperty that can be used as a prototype in a JComboBox etc.

    Mark A. Greenwood
